        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "{% comment %} ELIORA — Mécanisme d'action en 4 étapes (format Oren) {% endcomment %}\n\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,500&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n<style>\n  .eli-mec {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n    max-width: 640px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 8px 16px;\n    background: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__eyebrow-wrap {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__eyebrow-wrap > span {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.18em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #C9785B;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__eyebrow-line {\n    flex: 1;\n    height: 1px;\n    background: rgba(201,120,91,0.35);\n    max-width: 60px;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__title {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: clamp(24px,6vw,38px);\n    font-weight: 400;\n    line-height: 1.15;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n    margin: 0 0 8px;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__title em {\n    display: block;\n    font-style: italic;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #C9785B;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__subtitle {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #8A8178;\n    margin: 0 0 28px;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }\n  .eli-mec__step {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;\n    gap: 0;\n    background: #FFFFFF;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(26,26,26,0.08);\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    min-height: 120px;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__visual {\n    background: #F5ECD7;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    padding: 16px 10px 28px;\n    position: relative;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__visual svg { width: 100%; height: auto; max-width: 100px; }\n  .eli-mec__visual-caption {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 6px;\n    left: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 8.5px;\n    color: #A08C7A;\n    padding: 0 4px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__content {\n    padding: 16px 16px 16px 14px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__step-label {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.16em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #C9785B;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__step-title {\n    font-size: clamp(15px,2.5vw,19px);\n    font-weight: 400;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin: 0 0 6px;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__step-text {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    color: #4A4640;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n  .eli-mec__step-text strong { font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; }\n  .eli-mec__connector { display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 6px 0; }\n  .eli-mec__connector span {\n    width: 1px;\n    height: 16px;\n    background: #C9785B;\n    opacity: 0.6;\n    border-radius: 1px;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes float-up {\n    0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }\n    50% { transform: translateY(-5px); }\n  }\n  @keyframes pulse-scale {\n    0%,100% { transform: scale(1); }\n    50% { transform: scale(1.12); }\n  }\n  @keyframes drift {\n    0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n    25% { transform: translate(2px,-3px); }\n    50% { transform: translate(-2px,-5px); }\n    75% { transform: translate(-3px,-2px); }\n  }\n  @keyframes drift2 {\n    0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n    25% { transform: translate(-2px,-4px); }\n    50% { transform: translate(3px,-6px); }\n    75% { transform: translate(2px,-2px); }\n  }\n  @keyframes drift3 {\n    0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n    33% { transform: translate(3px,-4px); }\n    66% { transform: translate(-2px,-3px); }\n  }\n  @keyframes drift4 {\n    0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n    33% { transform: translate(-3px,-5px); }\n    66% { transform: translate(2px,-2px); }\n  }\n  @keyframes drift5 {\n    0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n    50% { transform: translate(1px,-4px); }\n  }\n  @keyframes spin-float {\n    0%,100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }\n    50% { transform: translateY(-4px) rotate(6deg); }\n  }\n  @keyframes appear-dot {\n    0%,100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(0.7); }\n    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }\n  }\n  @keyframes cross-fade {\n    0%,100% { opacity: 1; }\n    50% { opacity: 0.4; }\n  }\n  @keyframes smile-grow {\n    0%,100% { transform: scaleX(1); }\n    50% { transform: scaleX(1.15); }\n  }\n  @keyframes bar-grow1 {\n    0%,100% { transform: scaleY(1); }\n    50% { transform: scaleY(1.1); }\n  }\n  @keyframes bar-grow2 {\n    0%,100% { transform: scaleY(1); }\n    50% { transform: scaleY(1.18); }\n  }\n  @keyframes bar-grow3 {\n    0%,100% { transform: scaleY(1); }\n    50% { transform: scaleY(1.3); }\n  }\n  @keyframes dot-pulse {\n    0%,100% { r: 2.5; opacity: 0.7; }\n    50% { r: 3.5; opacity: 1; }\n  }\n\n  .anim-bubble1 { animation: drift  3.2s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  .anim-bubble2 { animation: drift2 2.8s ease-in-out infinite 0.3s; }\n  .anim-bubble3 { animation: drift3 3.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.6s; }\n  .anim-bubble4 { animation: drift4 2.6s ease-in-out infinite 0.9s; }\n  .anim-bubble5 { animation: drift5 3.8s ease-in-out infinite 0.4s; }\n  .anim-arrow  { animation: float-up 2.2s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  .anim-pill   { animation: spin-float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  .anim-dot1   { animation: appear-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  .anim-dot2   { animation: appear-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite 0.5s; }\n  .anim-dot3   { animation: appear-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite 1s; }\n  .anim-dot4   { animation: appear-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite 1.5s; }\n  .anim-cross1 { animation: cross-fade 2.4s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  .anim-cross2 { animation: cross-fade 2.4s ease-in-out infinite 0.8s; }\n  .anim-smile  { animation: smile-grow 2.8s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin: center; transform-box: fill-box; }\n  .anim-bar1   { animation: bar-grow1 2.5s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin: bottom; transform-box: fill-box; }\n  .anim-bar2   { animation: bar-grow2 2.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.4s; transform-origin: bottom; transform-box: fill-box; }\n  .anim-bar3   { animation: bar-grow3 2.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.8s; transform-origin: bottom; transform-box: fill-box; }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"eli-mec\">\n\n  <div class=\"eli-mec__eyebrow-wrap\">\n    <span class=\"eli-mec__eyebrow-line\"></span>\n    <span>Mécanisme d'action</span>\n    <span class=\"eli-mec__eyebrow-line\"></span>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2 class=\"eli-mec__title\">Comment Eliora <em>agit sur votre ventre.</em></h2>\n  <p class=\"eli-mec__subtitle\">4 étapes. De la gélule au confort digestif.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"eli-mec__steps\">\n\n    <div class=\"eli-mec__step\">\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__visual\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 80\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n          <ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"48\" rx=\"34\" ry=\"26\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-bubble1\" cx=\"38\" cy=\"37\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#E8C9B8\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-bubble2\" cx=\"56\" cy=\"30\" r=\"6.5\" fill=\"#E8C9B8\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-bubble3\" cx=\"67\" cy=\"48\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#E8C9B8\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-bubble4\" cx=\"35\" cy=\"56\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#E8C9B8\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-bubble5\" cx=\"55\" cy=\"60\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#E8C9B8\"/>\n          <g class=\"anim-arrow\">\n            <path d=\"M50 20 L50 12\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n            <path d=\"M46 16 L50 10 L54 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </g>\n        </svg>\n        <span class=\"eli-mec__visual-caption\">Gaz piégés dans l'intestin</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__content\">\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-label\">Étape 01</p>\n        <h3 class=\"eli-mec__step-title\">Les gaz s'accumulent</h3>\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-text\">Après le repas, les gaz intestinaux <strong>s'accumulent et distendent le ventre</strong>. C'est ce qui provoque la sensation de gonflement et d'inconfort.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-mec__connector\"><span></span></div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-mec__step\">\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__visual\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 80\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n          <g class=\"anim-pill\">\n            <ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"42\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"10\" fill=\"#1A1A1A\"/>\n            <text x=\"50\" y=\"46\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">eliora</text>\n          </g>\n          <circle class=\"anim-dot1\" cx=\"18\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#C9785B\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-dot2\" cx=\"82\" cy=\"20\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#C9785B\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-dot3\" cx=\"15\" cy=\"62\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#C9785B\"/>\n          <circle class=\"anim-dot4\" cx=\"85\" cy=\"62\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#C9785B\"/>\n          <text x=\"18\" y=\"11\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"6.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">Charbon</text>\n          <text x=\"82\" y=\"13\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"6.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">Fenouil</text>\n          <text x=\"15\" y=\"74\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"6.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">Gingembre</text>\n          <text x=\"85\" y=\"74\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"6.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">Actif</text>\n        </svg>\n        <span class=\"eli-mec__visual-caption\">Actifs libérés dans l'intestin</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__content\">\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-label\">Étape 02</p>\n        <h3 class=\"eli-mec__step-title\">La gélule libère ses actifs</h3>\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-text\">Charbon végétal, fenouil et gingembre se diffusent dans le système digestif et <strong>entrent directement en action</strong> sur les zones de gonflement.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-mec__connector\"><span></span></div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-mec__step\">\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__visual\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 80\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n          <ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"48\" rx=\"34\" ry=\"26\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/>\n          <circle cx=\"40\" cy=\"38\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#D9CDBE\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n          <circle cx=\"62\" cy=\"55\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#D9CDBE\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n          <g class=\"anim-cross1\">\n            <line x1=\"35\" y1=\"33\" x2=\"45\" y2=\"43\" stroke=\"#9E2A24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n            <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"33\" x2=\"35\" y2=\"43\" stroke=\"#9E2A24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          </g>\n          <g class=\"anim-cross2\">\n            <line x1=\"57\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"67\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"#9E2A24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n            <line x1=\"67\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"57\" y2=\"60\" stroke=\"#9E2A24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          </g>\n          <path class=\"anim-smile\" d=\"M38 64 a14 8 0 0 0 28 0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        </svg>\n        <span class=\"eli-mec__visual-caption\">Gaz captés · ventre apaisé</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__content\">\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-label\">Étape 03</p>\n        <h3 class=\"eli-mec__step-title\">Les gaz sont captés</h3>\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-text\">Le charbon végétal <strong>absorbe les gaz responsables des ballonnements</strong>, tandis que le fenouil et le gingembre détendent les parois intestinales.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-mec__connector\"><span></span></div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-mec__step\">\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__visual\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 80\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n          <line x1=\"10\" y1=\"66\" x2=\"90\" y2=\"66\" stroke=\"#D9CDBE\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/>\n\n          <circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"66\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#C9785B\"/>\n          <g class=\"anim-bar1\">\n            <path d=\"M22 60 Q22 54 28 52\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          </g>\n          <text x=\"22\" y=\"46\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">Moins de</text>\n          <text x=\"22\" y=\"53\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">ballonnements</text>\n\n          <circle cx=\"52\" cy=\"66\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#C9785B\"/>\n          <g class=\"anim-bar2\">\n            <path d=\"M47 60 Q47 48 52 40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n            <path d=\"M57 60 Q57 48 52 40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          </g>\n          <text x=\"52\" y=\"33\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">Digestion</text>\n          <text x=\"52\" y=\"40\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">apaisée</text>\n\n          <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"66\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#C9785B\"/>\n          <g class=\"anim-bar3\">\n            <path d=\"M74 60 Q74 40 80 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n            <path d=\"M80 60 Q80 40 80 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n            <path d=\"M86 60 Q86 40 80 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n          </g>\n          <text x=\"80\" y=\"17\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">Ventre plat</text>\n          <text x=\"80\" y=\"24\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#9C4F36\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">retrouvé</text>\n\n          <text x=\"22\" y=\"75\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#A08C7A\" text-anchor=\"middle\">J 1–3</text>\n          <text x=\"52\" y=\"75\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#A08C7A\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Sem. 1–2</text>\n          <text x=\"80\" y=\"75\" font-family=\"Poppins, sans-serif\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#A08C7A\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Sem. 3–4</text>\n        </svg>\n        <span class=\"eli-mec__visual-caption\">Évolution du confort digestif</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-mec__content\">\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-label\">Étape 04</p>\n        <h3 class=\"eli-mec__step-title\">Le confort s'installe</h3>\n        <p class=\"eli-mec__step-text\"><strong>Jours 1-3 :</strong> moins de ballonnements. <strong>Semaines 1-2 :</strong> digestion apaisée. <strong>Semaines 3-4 :</strong> ventre plat retrouvé durablement.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
        "background": "#ffffff",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    },
    "custom_liquid_XeGbcD": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "{% comment %} ELIORA — FAQ style Oren {% endcomment %}\n\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n<style>\n  .eli-faq {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;\n    max-width: 640px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 8px 16px 40px;\n    background: #FFFFFF;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__eyebrow-wrap {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__eyebrow-wrap > span {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.18em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #C9785B;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__eyebrow-line {\n    flex: 1;\n    height: 1px;\n    background: rgba(201,120,91,0.35);\n    max-width: 60px;\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__title {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: clamp(26px, 6vw, 38px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__title-italic {\n    display: block;\n    font-style: italic;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #C9785B;\n    font-size: clamp(24px, 5.5vw, 36px);\n  }\n  .eli-faq__subtitle {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #8A8178;\n    margin: 0 0 32px;\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__list {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 10px;\n    margin-bottom: 28px;\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__item {\n    border: 1px solid rgba(26,26,26,0.09);\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    background: #FFFFFF;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: border-color 0.25s;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__item.is-open {\n    border-color: rgba(201,120,91,0.3);\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__question {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    gap: 12px;\n    padding: 18px 18px 18px 20px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    user-select: none;\n    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__question-text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    line-height: 1.35;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n    margin: 0;\n    flex: 1;\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__chevron {\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    width: 32px;\n    height: 32px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: #F5ECD7;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    transition: background 0.25s, transform 0.3s;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__item.is-open .eli-faq__chevron {\n    background: #C9785B;\n    transform: rotate(180deg);\n  }\n  .eli-faq__chevron svg {\n    width: 14px;\n    height: 14px;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__chevron svg path {\n    stroke: #C9785B;\n    transition: stroke 0.25s;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__item.is-open .eli-faq__chevron svg path {\n    stroke: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__answer {\n    max-height: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.25s ease;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__item.is-open .eli-faq__answer {\n    max-height: 600px;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__answer-inner {\n    padding: 0 20px 20px;\n    font-size: 13.5px;\n    line-height: 1.65;\n    color: #4A4640;\n    border-top: 1px solid rgba(26,26,26,0.06);\n    padding-top: 14px;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__answer-inner strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__answer-inner .highlight {\n    color: #C9785B;\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n\n  .eli-faq__contact {\n    background: #FBF8F2;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(201,120,91,0.15);\n    border-radius: 18px;\n    padding: 28px 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__contact-title {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n    margin: 0 0 6px;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__contact-sub {\n    font-size: 13.5px;\n    color: #8A8178;\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__contact-btn {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 13px 36px;\n    border: 1.5px solid #C9785B;\n    border-radius: 50px;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.14em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #C9785B;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    background: transparent;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;\n    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\n  }\n  .eli-faq__contact-btn:hover {\n    background: #C9785B;\n    color: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"eli-faq\">\n\n  <div class=\"eli-faq__eyebrow-wrap\">\n    <span class=\"eli-faq__eyebrow-line\"></span>\n    <span>FAQ</span>\n    <span class=\"eli-faq__eyebrow-line\"></span>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2 class=\"eli-faq__title\">\n    Des questions ?\n    <em class=\"eli-faq__title-italic\">Nous avons les réponses.</em>\n  </h2>\n  <p class=\"eli-faq__subtitle\">Tout ce que vous devez savoir sur votre cure Eliora.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"eli-faq__list\">\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Quand vais-je voir les premiers résultats ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          <strong>Dès les premiers jours</strong>, vous pouvez ressentir une réduction des ballonnements après les repas. La digestion s'apaise progressivement au cours des <span class=\"highlight\">2 premières semaines</span>. Un ventre plus plat et un confort durable s'installent généralement entre la <strong>3e et la 4e semaine</strong> de cure.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Est-ce que Eliora crée une dépendance ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          <strong>Non.</strong> Eliora est composée d'<span class=\"highlight\">actifs naturels</span> (charbon végétal, fenouil, gingembre) qui ne créent aucune accoutumance ni dépendance. Vous pouvez arrêter la cure à tout moment sans effet de sevrage.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Est-ce que ça peut avoir des effets secondaires ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          <strong>Eliora est très bien tolérée.</strong> Le charbon végétal peut légèrement foncer les selles — c'est un effet normal et sans danger. En cas de traitement médical en cours, nous conseillons de prendre les gélules à distance des médicaments (2h d'intervalle minimum).\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Est-ce vegan et sans gluten ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          <strong>Oui, à 100 %.</strong> Eliora est <span class=\"highlight\">vegan, sans gluten, sans lactose</span> et sans allergènes majeurs. Les gélules sont d'origine végétale (HPMC). Formulée pour convenir au plus grand nombre.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Est-ce naturel et sans OGM ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          <strong>Oui.</strong> Tous les actifs d'Eliora sont d'<span class=\"highlight\">origine naturelle</span>, sans OGM, sans colorants ni conservateurs artificiels. Formulée en France avec des ingrédients sélectionnés pour leur pureté et leur efficacité.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Combien de gélules dois-je prendre et quand ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          La dose recommandée est de <strong>2 gélules par jour</strong>, à prendre <span class=\"highlight\">avant les repas principaux</span> avec un grand verre d'eau. En cas de ballonnements ponctuels, vous pouvez prendre 2 gélules supplémentaires après le repas.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Puis-je prendre Eliora avec d'autres compléments ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          <strong>Oui, dans la plupart des cas.</strong> Cependant, le charbon végétal peut réduire l'absorption d'autres substances. Si vous prenez des médicaments ou d'autres compléments, respectez un <span class=\"highlight\">intervalle de 2h minimum</span> entre les prises.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"eli-faq__item\">\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__question\">\n        <p class=\"eli-faq__question-text\">Est-ce que ça convient à tout le monde ?</p>\n        <span class=\"eli-faq__chevron\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M3 5L7 9L11 5\" stroke=\"#C9785B\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"eli-faq__answer\">\n        <div class=\"eli-faq__answer-inner\">\n          Eliora convient aux adultes souffrant de <span class=\"highlight\">ballonnements, gaz et inconforts digestifs</span>. Elle est déconseillée aux femmes enceintes ou allaitantes et aux enfants. En cas de pathologie digestive diagnostiquée, consultez votre médecin avant de commencer une cure.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"eli-faq__contact\">\n    <p class=\"eli-faq__contact-title\">Une autre question ?</p>\n    <p class=\"eli-faq__contact-sub\">Notre équipe vous répond sous 24h, en français.</p>\n    <a href=\"mailto:contact@eliora.fr\" class=\"eli-faq__contact-btn\">Nous écrire</a>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  document.querySelectorAll('.eli-faq__question').forEach(function(btn) {\n    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      var item = btn.closest('.eli-faq__item');\n      var isOpen = item.classList.contains('is-open');\n      document.querySelectorAll('.eli-faq__item.is-open').forEach(function(el) {\n        el.classList.remove('is-open');\n      });\n      if (!isOpen) {\n        item.classList.add('is-open');\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>",
